or I'm meant to be at least, 

00:00:05.220 --> 00:00:09.900
but I've always felt like I identify
more with sleepy old men 

00:00:09.900 --> 00:00:11.710
than I do with the
"youth" of today.

00:00:11.710 --> 00:00:12.710
And this isn't all
young people, 

00:00:12.710 --> 00:00:16.160
but your stereotypical
18- to 25-year-old,

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:22.010
who goes to lots of parties and has a lot of fun
and says the word YOLO a lot, 

00:00:22.010 --> 00:00:23.210
I find them
very confusing. 

00:00:23.210 --> 00:00:27.080
However, back in October, I found
myself doing one of those things 

00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:28.500
that crazy
young people do, 

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:30.970
and I went on a road trip
around Europe 

00:00:30.970 --> 00:00:35.230
with a bunch of fun loving YouTube
kids because, you know what, 

00:00:35.230 --> 00:00:37.200
you do only
live once. SIGH

